VINCULOS.OUTRAS-INFORMACOES-INGLES:
Trainee by Robert Bosch GmbH, Stuttgart, Germany (http://tinyurl.com/8l2q5lm)
(http://tinyurl.com/8jo5bqc).

Developed activities:

- Construction of a robotic mechanism able to translate a Laser Doppler interferometer and Hot-Wire-Anemometry sensors along 3 orthogonal axes, used to investigate acoustic fields properties using Laser-Doppler Interferometry;

- Configuration of an optical environment for the realization of experimental measurements and numerical analysis;

- Calibration of mono-, bi- and tri-dimensional Hot-Wire Anemometry sensors;

- Execution of experimental investigations using Hot-Wire Anemometry and Laser-Scanning Interferometry;

- Support to the construction of a new environment for Laser mechanisms.
